      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so you can count on it for all your upcoming adventures! It runs smoothly and looks great, perfect for anyone looking for a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
