    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus. This driver-focused example is equipped with the G96/01 6-speed manual transaxle, delivering power through a precise shift linkage to the rear wheels. The chassis remains taut, utilizing MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry for exceptional kinematic feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes an upgraded IMS bearing and rear main seal to ensure long-term reliability. The braking system features four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, offering consistent thermal management. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical integrity is robust, providing linear power delivery and high lateral grip. This is a technically sound specimen for the purist who prioritizes performance and mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
