    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep luster, showing only the expected minor road chips and light surface marks consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium upholstery remains supple with minimal bolster wear, and every button, switch, and climate control function operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced on a strict schedule, featuring recent fluid changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires with plenty of tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. This is an honest, dependable car that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer. It\u2019s the ideal choice for a discerning driver seeking a high-quality experience and a vehicle that has been treated with respect since day one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
