    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? This beauty has been well-loved and is in really solid shape. It\u2019s got plenty of life left, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. I've taken great care of it, and it shows! Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it feels behind the wheel!",
