    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical suite is robust, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul already completed. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag 420G manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. To address common chassis fatigue, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with steel plates. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the suspension geometry remains tight and the throttle response is sharp. This is a mechanically sound, analog machine ready for technical backroads.",
